Summary: A letter from the Gemeentelijke Ombudsman to the wethouder Jeugdzaken en Educatie of Amsterdam, discussing the pilot ombudsman and Calvijn met Junior College, and the importance of parental involvement in school procedures.

It also mentions the sharing of positive experiences and best practices among schools, and the involvement of the Kinderombudsman in school matters.
